title: Ep 116 - Invest in Yourself (KNOWLEDGE IS POWER PT. 4)
itunes:title: Ep 116 - Invest in Yourself (KNOWLEDGE IS POWER PT. 4)
description:
Part Four of the Knowledge is Power Series is "Invest in Yourself" The trouble with most people's mindsets today is that they have have no trouble spending a couple hundred dollars on drinks each weekend but when it comes to investing into their own knowledge they get cheap. Investing in your own self development is the most surefire way to get a massive return on your investment and in this episode I talk about why.
